en\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2510}, {\"ngram\": \"the Teahupo'o challenge\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"the ledge\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's inspiring.\\\"\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Picklum's team-mate Ethan Ewing knows all about the challenge of this place but still can not hide his smile as he prepares to start his event, 12 months after a huge wipeout broke his back here.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picklum's team-mate Ethan Ewing\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"this place\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"his smile\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"his event\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge wipeout\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"his back\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just one of those waves, it's got big consequences,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those waves\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"big consequences\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The energy of this wave is like nothing else, it's just so raw and has so much power.\\\"\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The energy\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"this wave\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"so much power\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Five-time world champion Carissa Moore is back to defend her Olympic women's title but takes on a stacked field, including Tahitian Vahin\\u00e9 Fierro and Brazil's Tatiana Weston-Webb, who scored a perfect ten on the Teahupo'o break in May.\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3225, 